<lj-cut text="here i am, rip me apart">
Name:ashley 
Age:14
Sex:female
Location:toledo, ohio
Date of first MCR show:march 8th
What were your feelings/reactions:Well, it was my first concert so I was really flippin' happy and all but then on top of that I was going to see my favorite band so I felt like crying. I know it sounds really corny but I don't care thats how I felt. Then when My Chemical Romance performed I screamed every word in unison with the audience and it was amazing. Normally I am kinda self-conscious but that night I felt ok with doing what I wanted to support the guys because I knew I wasn't the only one that felt that way.
Favorite member:Well, that's kinda hard...but I would have to say Gerard because i know he had a problem with depression, anti-depressants and slcohol and he stared MCR to help better himself and his situation. Also, I love to sing and his voice is amazing. :)
Favorite album & song:I only have '3 Cheers For Sweet Revenge' and i can't pick a fave. I love them all.
How long have you been a fan?:Mm, not that long about 5 months. I know its not really that long.
What MCR merch do you own (posting pics would be great):I have the 3 Cheers album shirt and i have the 3 cheers cd and i have Gerard's backstage pass! long story, i wasn't the lucky one to meet him. :(
What do you think of the "newer" fans:Well, I'm a pretty new fan myself so I really wouldn't think about  that but it really shouldn't matter how long you have been a fan, it should be about the music and supporting the guys.
Have you met them? If so, what were they like?:No, not yet anyways. :(
Why are you so devoted?:
Post some pictures of yourself:sorry i would but i have a crappy computer and no camera. i'll try to get my friends to help me there.

Please specify if you want to be a member, or co-mod(I think three are enough for now).

2. Then, beside numbers 1 and 2, write down any
